      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580159&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1116&rangeEnd=1137",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7e73277071e1dfff7e755df?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1116&rangeEnd=1137"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580159_3_1827-1902",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1827-1902",
      "markText": "如果我们仅仅了解其间善良的一面而不了解邪恶的一面，那就会把世界看得很美好，把所有的人都当作仁人君子，这实际上不是一种可爱的天真，而只是一种愚蠢的幼稚。",
      "totalCount": 260,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580159&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1827&rangeEnd=1902",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7e73277071e1dfff7e755df?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1827&rangeEnd=1902"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580159_3_412-471",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "412-471",
      "markText": "大凡人们需要的东西，才可能在社会上具有强大的生命力。反言之，具有强大的生命力而能经久不衰的，也必定是对人们有用的东西。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31580159&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=412&rangeEnd=471",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7e73277071e1dfff7e755df?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=412&rangeEnd=471"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "31580159_18_5788-5820",
      "chapterUid": 18,
